    <item>
      <title>特朗普律师开启封口费辩护攻击科恩和丹尼尔斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-lawyer-opens-hush-money-defense-attacking-cohen-daniels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师在这场历史性审判中展开刑事辩护，试图抹黑关键证人，并辩称检察官错误地指控这位前总统通过付钱给色情明星斯托米·丹尼尔斯来掩盖她的性关系指控，从而破坏了 2016 年的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-lawyer-opens-hush-money-defense-attacking-cohen-daniels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 19:10:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥奥夫拉多尔淡化候选人高速公路劫持后的暴力行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/mexico-s-amlo-downplays-violence-after-sheinbaum-highway-holdup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔淡化了周末发生的该党候选人在高速公路上被蒙面男子拦截的事件，并指责媒体和民间组织夸大选举期间的暴力行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/mexico-s-amlo-downplays-violence-after-sheinbaum-highway-holdup</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 17:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登告诉泽伦斯基，一旦参议院投票，乌克兰援助将迅速到位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/biden-tells-zelenskiy-aid-will-flow-quickly-once-senate-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登告诉乌克兰总统泽伦斯基，如果参议院本周投票批准一项包括向基辅提供 610 亿美元的援助计划，他的政府将迅速采取行动分发安全援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/biden-tells-zelenskiy-aid-will-flow-quickly-once-senate-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 17:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snap 倾向于利用选举报道来竞标政治广告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/snap-leans-into-election-coverage-in-bid-for-political-ads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap Inc. 倾向于报道美国大选，利用其深厚的合格选民用户群，尽管规模更大的竞争对手 Meta Platforms Inc. 淡化了其社交媒体网站上政治内容的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/snap-leans-into-election-coverage-in-bid-for-political-ads</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列尚未提供加沙联合国工作人员与哈马斯有联系的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/israel-yet-to-offer-proof-un-staff-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据外部调查结果，以色列尚未提供证据证明加沙地带联合国救援机构的工作人员与恐怖组织有广泛联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/israel-yet-to-offer-proof-un-staff-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国脱欧后出口商品减少，经济向服务业倾斜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/uk-exports-fewer-goods-after-brexit-tilting-economy-to-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方数据显示，由于英国经济更加依赖向世界其他地区销售服务，英国的出口商品仍少于脱欧前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/uk-exports-fewer-goods-after-brexit-tilting-economy-to-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:16:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西的财政困境加大了卢拉财务主管的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/brazil-s-fiscal-woes-test-lula-s-trust-in-his-political-heir</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从监狱到总统职位，巴西的路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦在需要的时候比其他任何人都更愿意求助于一个盟友：费尔南多·哈达德，他任命为财政部长，曾经也是未来可能的政治继承人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/brazil-s-fiscal-woes-test-lula-s-trust-in-his-political-heir</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在最高法院的豁免策略：拖延仍然是胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-s-immunity-case-at-supreme-court-a-delay-means-a-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院对唐纳德·特朗普声称因试图推翻 2020 年选举而获得刑事指控豁免的历史性考虑遇到了严峻的现实：日历与宪法一样重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-s-immunity-case-at-supreme-court-a-delay-means-a-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国逮捕三名涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动的嫌疑人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/germany-arrests-three-suspected-of-spying-for-chinese-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国当局逮捕了两名男子和一名女子，他们涉嫌为中国国家安全工作，以获取船舶发动机技术的详细信息，并在未经出口授权的情况下购买特殊激光器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/germany-arrests-three-suspected-of-spying-for-chinese-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:44:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
